    <h2 class="f2 lh-subtitle mt0 pt0">
      Privacy Vulnerabilities in the Peer-to-Peer Network of Cryptocurrencies
    </h2>
    <div class="fn w-100 mt4 mb4 pt3-ns pt1">
      <div class="aspect-ratio aspect-ratio--16x9">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BwFUUWkp8YQ" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; encrypted-media; gyroscope" allowfullscreen class="aspect-ratio--object"></iframe>
      </div>
